<!--
  .22 LR Ammunition Definitions - CENTRALIZED
  Used by ALL .22 LR rimfire pistols (Walther P22, SIG P22, FN 502, PMR-30)

  RIMFIRE CARTRIDGE - LOWEST POWER HANDGUN ROUND:
  Pistol barrels (3-5") produce 200-400 fps LESS than advertised rifle specs
  Actual energy: 80-115 ft-lbs from pistol barrels (compare: 9mm = 350-400 ft-lbs)

  TERMINAL BALLISTICS NOTE:
  - Hollow points RARELY expand from pistol-length barrels
  - Penetration rather than expansion drives terminal effect
  - High headshot multipliers compensate for low base damage

  FMJ (Standard - CCI Mini-Mag): 12-15 dmg base, 0.50 pen, ~1,000 fps
    - 40gr round nose/solid, 12-15" gel penetration
    - Reliable cycling in semi-autos
    - Good for suppressor use

  JHP (High Velocity - CCI Velocitor): +20% dmg, 0.35 pen, ~1,100 fps
    - 40gr HP, 15-16" penetration but MINIMAL expansion from short barrels
    - Lucky Gunner testing: CCI Velocitor = 0" expansion, 15.58" penetration
    - Higher energy compensates, reduced barrier performance

  PMR-30 NOTE: Uses .22 WMR ballistics (~160 ft-lbs) but same ammo system
  for gameplay simplicity. Damage differentiation in weapon stats.

  Load this resource BEFORE any .22 LR weapon resources in server.cfg:
    ensure ammo_system_standalone
    ensure weapon_p22
    ensure weapon_sig_p22
    ensure weapon_fn502
    ensure weapon_pmr30
    ...
-->
